== Naubino

=== Run
# one of the following, depends
python plain.py
python3 plain.py
python2 plain.py # Ubuntu Lucid Lynx

=== Dependencies
* Python 3.1 >
** and every python specific dependency also build with and for python 3
** try "2to3"

# also possible, see Ubuntu Lucid Lynx Build Manual
* Python 2.6 >

* PyQt4 
** Qt 4.6 >

* pymunk 1.0.0
** chipmunk 5.3.2

=== Build
==== Ubuntu Lucid Lynx
sudo aptitude install git-core python-setuptools python3.1 python-qt4

# choose one:
# needs python2.7, not included in Ubuntu Lucid Lynx
#sudo easy_install 3to2 # not testet
sudo easy_install 3to2_py3k pymunk

git clone git://gitorious.org/cute-naubino/cute-naubino.git
cd cute-naubino

# choose one:
# already converted version, maybe outdated
git checkout py2
# convert yourself, maybe buggy
#git checkout -b py2
#git merge -s theirs master
#3to2 -w *py

